<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa ah kipak un! A lungsiet pakchau,
 Sala tangte ei pawt sak tai;
 A thisana tatsa bang di'n I lau dem?
 Isu I &quot;Bangcheng&quot; hi ngala.

[V2]
 &quot;Pathien I lama A pan chun,
 Pathien in ei panpih chun;
 Kuo a ei do thei ding? ..... kuo? ..... kuo? ..... kuo?
 Kuo a ei do thei ding, do thei ding?

[V3]
 2. Lalpa ah hat un, A theihna kipak un,
 Nicheng in ginum in um un;
 Setan hun thep tieng thudik chuh panpih un,
 Amah chuh I hatnau hi'n a.

[V4]
 3. A thu ging un A thutiem a thawn ngei puoi,
 Krista achun ahi, Amen;
 Lei hi mang mahleh A thutiem mang puona,
 Zie chuh Bible ah a chuong hi.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa ah um un, Amah thu chun nung un,
 Kumkhuo hinna bul chuh ahi;
 Thagau hatlo kithing Amah khuta um,
 Kuoman sulawk thei tapuo'n a!</lyrics>
<title>&quot;IF GOD BE FOR US&quot;</title>
<hymn_number>313</hymn_number>
</song>